dc_title_s: EMS Response Districts Manitowoc County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: [Public safety responding territories, including ambulance, fire, first responder, jaws, and police districts in Manitowoc County, Wisconsin. Combined into beats and ORIs for use in the computer-aided dispatching software used by the Manitowoc County Joint Dispatch Center.]This data layer represents Emergency Medical Service (EMS) response districts in Manitowoc County, Wisconsin in 2020.
uw_supplemental_s: Augment original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
